we can get data from a pipeline 
this pipeline is the data_pipe_extract_features.py

and example of the useing this is 
cat AI_text/meta1.txt | python3 data_pipe_extract_features.py -AI -schema -pipe > data.csv

this will pipe the data into a csv 
the -schema will print the schema for the csv so if you would like to append to this we can do this

cat  -s <AI_text_file_name.txt>| python3 data_pipe_extract_features.py -AI -pipe >> data.csv
or
cat -s <human_text_file_name.txt>| python3 data_pipe_extract_features.py -human -pipe >> data.csv
